            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/dragon-age-the-veilguard-is-only-40-right-now/1100-6528756/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div id="site-main">

      
                    
  
