          <p>
    <span data-nosnippet="">GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links.</span>
  </p>
  
    <article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6528756">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Last year saw plenty of great games released, and if you're looking to catch up on Dragon Age: The Veilguard, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dragon-Age-Veilguard-PlayStation-5/dp/B0DCMN43SC?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">you can get it for just $40 right now through Amazon</a>. After an ill-fated trip into live-service territory with Anthem, BioWare's return to its single-player roots was well-received when it released last year, and the game checks all the boxes for a fun fantasy adventure. In case it sells out at Amazon, <a href="https://howl.link/y16sifxfj9dk0?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17367652689719?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">you can also grab it for this price at Best Buy</a>.</p><div title="6528756 - Dragon Age: The Veilguard" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="3054" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6528756 - Dragon Age: The Veilguard" data-collection="">             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dragon-Age-Veilguard-PlayStation-5/dp/B0DCMN43SC?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Dragon-Age-Veilguard-PlayStation-5\/dp\/B0DCMN43SC?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Dragon-Age-Veilguard-PlayStation-5/dp/B0DCMN43SC?tag=gamespot-promos-20">Dragon Age: The Veilguard</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dragon-Age-Veilguard-PlayStation-5/dp/B0DCMN43SC?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Dragon-Age-Veilguard-PlayStation-5\/dp\/B0DCMN43SC?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Dragon-Age-Veilguard-PlayStation-5/dp/B0DCMN43SC?tag=gamespot-promos-20">$40</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>While it's not a groundbreaking game like previous entries in the series, Dragon Age: The Veilguard still shows just how good BioWare is at crafting an adventure set in a magical world and bolstered by strong real-time action-based combat. "Inch by inch, The Veilguard has wormed its way into my Inquisition-loving heart. Is The Veilguard as complex and nuanced as past Dragon Age games? No, not at all. Instead, it delivers an action-packed romp through a fantastical setting with good friends," Jordan Ram√©e wrote in GameSpot's <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/dragon-age-the-veilguard-review/1900-6418294/" data-ref-id="1900-6418294">Dragon Age: The Veilguard review</a>. </p>                      </div><p>If you're looking to add a few more trinkets from Thedas to your collection, you can also pick up the official <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Art-Dragon-Age-Veilguard/dp/1506732968?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dragon Age: The Veilguard art book for $40</a> (was $50). This is a 256-page oversized book showing off concept art and final designs, covering everything from characters to weapons, and if you really feel like splurging, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1506732984?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">then you can pick up the deluxe edition for $100</a>. This package includes the book inside of an elegant foil-stamped slipcase and cover, gilded pages, a ribbon book marker, and two lithographic art prints housed inside of a sleek portfolio.</p><h2>Dragon Age Art Books and Graphic Novels</h2><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4426292-dragon-age-art-book.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4426292" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1280" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4426292-dragon-age-art-book.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4426292"></a><figcaption>The Art of Dragon Age: The Veilguard</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4426292-dragon-age-art-book.jpg"></figure><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Art-Dragon-Age-Veilguard/dp/1506732968?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Art of Dragon Age: The Veilguard</a> -- $40 ($<del>50</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1506732984?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Art of Dragon Age: The Veilguard (Deluxe Edition)</a> -- $100</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dragon-Age-World-Thedas-Boxed/dp/1506736882?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dragon Age: Graphic Novel Collection</a> -- $50 ($<del>60</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BNVZK359?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dragon Age: The Official Cookbook</a> -- $32.50 ($<del>35</del>)</li></ul><p>There's also a collection of two paperback <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dragon-Age-World-Thedas-Boxed/dp/1506736882?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dragon Age graphic novels</a> on sale for $50 (was $60), and if you're hungry for fantasy, the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BNVZK359?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">official Dragon Age cookbook</a> will give you a taste of Thedas for only $32.50 (was $35).</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
